{"tid":2487793,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇人覺得投廢票影響大過唔投票","createTime":"2021-04-13T23:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:39:47.000Z","uid":109462,"like":34,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"784389a1bf69b36a0615e6ccaf8b5bdb241c1b78","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"3月9號有個報道，係林鄭喺記者會度表示唔會為呢一次「政改」做諮詢，原因係「市民唔關心立法會」。如果投票人數低落，政府就更加振振有辭話「市民已對政治厭倦」，再引用其他民主國家投票率低嘅例子混淆視聽（日本2019年參議院選舉投票率可以低過50%）。<br />\n<br />\n如果集中投廢票，甚至開出嚟廢票多過有效票，呢個就係最實在嘅數字，唔需要再多花唇舌解釋。<br />\n<br />\n成件事個效果係一來可以量化展示香港人意志，令大家知道大家仲喺度、仍然堅持，鼓舞同路士氣；二來國際宣傳上亦比較容易操作，唔使再特登解釋話投票率低係源於抵制投票而唔係市民對政治厭倦。"},{"pid":"ce3929a329a2d944c83d33da7de06d207b00d9b9","tid":2487793,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:23:11.000Z","msg":"重點係林鄭老細習近平唔會理西方國家嘅態度，佢認為就算同西方國家為敵，中國都係最終勝利者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/talkshows/vharbor/lktk2-03192021150816.html/@@images/image/social_media\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Ftalkshows%2Fvharbor%2Flktk2-03192021150816.html%2F%40%40images%2Fimage%2Fsocial_media&h=73cbdb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV3Lq3CyatiJypteTszVwTVGszj1SMH8r9kMrxxLXyJt5?filename=kEfH2Xe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEfH2Xe.jpg&h=a09a0c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kdf4Wdf52Tg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fkdf4Wdf52Tg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=27d86217&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ab3d644ba841fe124d68186b771ce026f74ffe7","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:24:31.000Z","msg":"林鄭拒政改諮詢：市民唔關心&emsp;<br />\n民主進程大倒退&emsp;學者料更不信任政府<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2021.03.09 02:00<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京以「完善」為名，將由全國人大出手大改香港立法會選舉及特首選委選舉的組成。剛由北京返港的特首林鄭月娥強調，人大修例合憲合法，毋須啟動政改五部曲及由立會通過，又稱選委會提名立會議員安排非過渡性，並以<strong><span class=\"red\">「市民現時對立法會唔係好關心」</span></strong>，拒再諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=087f1847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&h=60b5e8f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc</a>"},{"pid":"e3a63f67c732fe69ec676ae6c643aa61d7f186a3","tid":2487793,"uid":56107,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:26:38.000Z","msg":"其實如果唔取消選民登記嘅話，就一定要去投廢票<br />\n登記咗又唔投嘅話，你個名就會有人拎去幫你投紫荊黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38c2f9f176f55ec133dee2eab269dbb05d9b462","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce3929a329a2d944c83d33da7de06d207b00d9b9","tid":2487793,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:23:11.000Z","msg":"重點係林鄭老細習近平唔會理西方國家嘅態度，佢認為就算同西方國家為敵，中國都係最終勝利者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/talkshows/vharbor/lktk2-03192021150816.html/@@images/image/social_media\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Ftalkshows%2Fvharbor%2Flktk2-03192021150816.html%2F%40%40images%2Fimage%2Fsocial_media&h=73cbdb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEfH2Xe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEfH2Xe.jpg&h=a09a0c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kdf4Wdf52Tg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fkdf4Wdf52Tg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=27d86217&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:27:11.000Z","msg":"所以我講嗰兩個效果都唔係俾共產黨睇，係俾我哋自己人睇同埋俾國際社會睇，尤其是我覺得有一個實際數字出嚟，反映到大家嘅意志、鼓舞到香港人嘅士氣，都係一個好重要嘅考慮點<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ab489c5d76786377af495d935f4cc816deac2","tid":2487793,"uid":194120,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"越多人排隊投票越有利政府做票,癈票白票都可以用預先準備好嘅票代替,製造[完善選舉制度]得市民支持嘅假像欺騙全世界.<br />\n必須全面杯葛令票站鬼影都冇！等佢做假都要柒出世界。"},{"pid":"3030c0c30658c330ac833c069bc264a450b3c327","tid":2487793,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351ab489c5d76786377af495d935f4cc816deac2","tid":2487793,"uid":194120,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"越多人排隊投票越有利政府做票,癈票白票都可以用預先準備好嘅票代替,製造[完善選舉制度]得市民支持嘅假像欺騙全世界.<br />\n必須全面杯葛令票站鬼影都冇！等佢做假都要柒出世界。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:40:39.000Z","msg":"香港有4成藍絲，全港70%最大投票率，入面嘅40%出嚟投，咁都有28%投票率，唔會鬼影都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575a2faa9e84164eb8c963c581ec202c8b9d6d00","tid":2487793,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"351ab489c5d76786377af495d935f4cc816deac2","tid":2487793,"uid":194120,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"越多人排隊投票越有利政府做票,癈票白票都可以用預先準備好嘅票代替,製造[完善選舉制度]得市民支持嘅假像欺騙全世界.<br />\n必須全面杯葛令票站鬼影都冇！等佢做假都要柒出世界。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:49:42.000Z","msg":"咁多鐵票「鐵人」，無可能喎&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"42bc1314529706305c1ad9028f9b12b712fe39f0","tid":2487793,"uid":192465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:53:12.000Z","msg":"老實講就算有50%廢票今時今日又wfc?"},{"pid":"db4716940589cdadbadbd9368e571a157f91afd2","tid":2487793,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":