000Z","msg":"就算佢得 5%投票率 ，只要5%入面投保蝗党有90%佢都可以大大聲話 ，&ldquo;9成市民&rdquo;支持正苦 依法c政，香港遊說團體未少左個重要參考來同外國政府傾香港事囉"},{"pid":"4681063facfb0aff9cb7883a1bfc11555f7fe2bc","tid":2487793,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab3d644ba841fe124d68186b771ce026f74ffe7","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:24:31.000Z","msg":"林鄭拒政改諮詢：市民唔關心&emsp;<br />\n民主進程大倒退&emsp;學者料更不信任政府<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2021.03.09 02:00<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京以「完善」為名，將由全國人大出手大改香港立法會選舉及特首選委選舉的組成。剛由北京返港的特首林鄭月娥強調，人大修例合憲合法，毋須啟動政改五部曲及由立會通過，又稱選委會提名立會議員安排非過渡性，並以<strong><span class=\"red\">「市民現時對立法會唔係好關心」</span></strong>，拒再諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=087f1847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&h=60b5e8f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:44:31.000Z","msg":"屌原來我唔係市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8975b178fa5d8cb05d6795d07620535d7527a538","tid":2487793,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4681063facfb0aff9cb7883a1bfc11555f7fe2bc","tid":2487793,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab3d644ba841fe124d68186b771ce026f74ffe7","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:24:31.000Z","msg":"林鄭拒政改諮詢：市民唔關心&emsp;<br />\n民主進程大倒退&emsp;學者料更不信任政府<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2021.03.09 02:00<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京以「完善」為名，將由全國人大出手大改香港立法會選舉及特首選委選舉的組成。剛由北京返港的特首林鄭月娥強調，人大修例合憲合法，毋須啟動政改五部曲及由立會通過，又稱選委會提名立會議員安排非過渡性，並以<strong><span class=\"red\">「市民現時對立法會唔係好關心」</span></strong>，拒再諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=087f1847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210309%2FBM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc&h=60b5e8f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210309/BM7SAKHVQ5CJ3CX4TKQSYFEFLU/?fbclid=IwAR1-40iAi6LlbiM91mhdaRwvgCjwxYYMQenSYm_U_Inu-zQdVORZDgUVbGc</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:44:31.000Z","msg":"屌原來我唔係市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"推返"},{"pid":"8df5b33dd350f3b0d7d2b275258fead85dbf1a70","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1109a59c363d13e298fad32a8aea9b50bbc24c","tid":2487793,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"236af828a48ae3d5e3def73d8b793ff4d7bfcae9","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63419df5c1abf9b9ef991878f2f0ef84e887db2","tid":2487793,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"對個政府毫無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接移民仲好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起身拎到錢走對佢影響更大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:13:56.000Z","msg":"唔係個個一時三刻走得曬㗎嘛，咁一日仲喺度一日都要盡力試下做㗎啦，無論係影響政府、連結國際，抑或激勵人心，好過坐喺度等運到。有邊個唔想一下打爆機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"但你既論點完全冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇實際作用仲要搏比人用國安法告"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"個作用就係激勵人心同埋俾料國際輿論，如何維持士氣都係一個好重要嘅課題；去到今時今日你幾可可以有一個方法個作用大到可以立即直擊政權？就算移民真係好似你咁講有咁大威力，都要一段相當長嘅時間先見到慢性效果啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d035018ebf19539c0406c9d0011e774aafdf1c3","tid":2487793,"uid":329415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"784389a1bf69b36a0615e6ccaf8b5bdb241c1b78","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:18:51.000Z","msg":"3月9號有個報道，係林鄭喺記者會度表示唔會為呢一次「政改」做諮詢，原因係「市民唔關心立法會」。如果投票人數低落，政府就更加振振有辭話「市民已對政治厭倦」，再引用其他民主國家投票率低嘅例子混淆視聽（日本2019年參議院選舉投票率可以低過50%）。<br />\n<br />\n如果集中投廢票，甚至開出嚟廢票多過有效票，呢個就係最實在嘅數字，唔需要再多花唇舌解釋。<br />\n<br />\n成件事個效果係一來可以量化展示香港人意志，令大家知道大家仲喺度、仍然堅持，鼓舞同路士氣；二來國際宣傳上亦比較容易操作，唔使再特登解釋話投票率低係源於抵制投票而唔係市民對政治厭倦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"唔投最好，咁辛苦排隊投癈票做乜，投完都可能換曬票箱啦。"},{"pid":"77c55a17cc8def119749f3b3df9e919be1958e5f","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88dccfbefeb366858a515912535f0202446c3fb5","tid":2487793,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"就算佢得 5%投票率 ，只要5%入面投保蝗党有90%佢都可以大大聲話 ，&ldquo;9成市民&rdquo;支持正苦 依法c政，香港遊說團體未少左個重要參考來同外國政府傾香港事囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:48:09.000Z","msg":"所以我認為龐大嘅廢票數字可以更清晰地俾國際社會了解到香港大多數人嘅立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7805b4cb83aac6f741c14c3ebbafe33bf293c831","tid":2487793,"uid":331590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"係任何情況, 支港都可以9 UP/9 改投票結果<br />\n投唔投都係一樣"},{"pid":"3038c55897e87560f7cc21a058b4302f35e3c7a5","tid":2487793,"uid":109462,"